1. Download QE v7.4.1 from Gitlab:
   https://gitlab.com/QEF/q-e/-/tags

2. Uncompress the file:
   tar xvf qe-7.4.1.tar

3. Install the Gfortran compiler:
   sudo apt update
   sudo apt install gfortran

4. Install OpenMPI:
   sudo apt install openmpi-bin libopenmpi-dev

5. Configure QE:
   ./configure MPIF90=mpif90 F90=gfortran BLAS_LIBS="-lblas" LAPACK_LIBS="-llapack"

6. Install various codes of QE:
   make all

7. Add the path to executables to the environment:
   vi ~/.bashrc
   export PATH=$PATH:<path-to-qe-bin>
   save a close the file
   source ~/.bashrc

8. Test:
   type pw.x in a terminal
